tip.text: A NYC must.Many of the flowers beds are replanted for Spring and again in Summer so they are ever changing. Come at end of May - might be lucky to get some flower 'giveaways!' when the season changes.
The mango pudding is the most divine dessert. A beautiful mixture of textures and flavours.
